title: Everything Serves His Plan | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Everything Serves His Plan | Joel Osteen
description:
God can use setbacks and delays to move us into our purpose. He knows how to work everything together for your good. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
